---
Regression for #479: a multi-file commons (`money`, split across `cents.bynk` +
`label.bynk`) whose refined type crosses a cross-Worker boundary. Under
`--target workers` the boundary codec (`serialise_Cents`/`deserialise_Cents`)
must be emitted exactly once, in the file that declares `Cents` (`cents.ts`) —
never orphaned into the sibling `label.ts`, which has neither the type nor its
imports in scope.
---
context api

uses money

service check {
  on call(c: Cents) -> Effect[Int] {
    Effect.pure(0)
  }
}
